WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.917
Setting up a class takes minutes.

00:00:01.917 --> 00:00:04.472
On the home screen you choose “I'm a trainer

00:00:04.472 --> 00:00:09.002
create a new class”, enter the IEFP email, the class number and your password.

00:00:09.002 --> 00:00:12.545
From there, you import trainees from Excel and share the link

00:00:12.545 --> 00:00:14.520
each one enters their own sandbox.
